    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The exterior shows its age with several large dents, noticeable rust spots on the rocker panels, and a clear coat that is peeling extensively across the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears in the seating and a cracked dashboard. Mechanically, the car runs but suffers from a rough idle and an undiagnosed transmission slip, making it most suitable for a dedicated hobbyist looking for a full restoration project or a reliable source of salvageable parts.",
